   Special Series

The Book Ahead

   Our weekly peek at what's publishing

     * [61]Subscribe to Books Newsletter

   [62]Clockwise from top left, book covers of: Among Friends; Audition;
   Fahrenheit-182; King of Ashes; "Make It Ours"; Mark Twain; Toni at
   Random; Vanishing World; Vera Wong's Guide to Snooping (on a Dead Man);
   When Javi Dumped Mari
   NPR

Review

[63]10 books we're looking forward to this spring

   [64]April 2, 2025  A famed graphic novelist returns! A Southern-gothic
   crime-thriller inspired by The Godfather! An extremely in depth
   biography of Mark Twain! And more!

10 books we're looking forward to this spring

